Text.string: Do you have a moment to talk about the Twin Gods?
Oh, just you wait till I get more rockets in this thing!
Blessed are the meek for they are not full of bullets!
This isn't how it's supposed to go!
Why do the Calypsos forsake us?
You are an affront to Tyreen!
Watch out! We're all gonna die!
Tyreen, protect us from that abomination!
The beast comes for us! Kill it!
Not the hair, not the hair!
That iron will not save you!
I want one of those for Mercenary Day!
Twin kills for the Twin Gods!
We give thanks for this bounty!
You'll see the Great Vault soon!
Die with the Twin Gods' favor!
It was always going to end this way!
I see it... the Great... Vault...
I die, that the family may live...
This is what I'm gonna do to you!
Imagine your skull where my gun is!
Hey Vault Thief, you DOWN TO PAR-TAY?
I will be the last face you see!
Now's the time to repent, Vault Thief!
Oh yeah! Another sacrifice to the Gods!
I'm the frickin' CHAMPION OF TYREEN!
I got 'em! Tell me somebody saw that!
Tyreen, we're getting massacred! Save us!
May the Twin Gods renew our numbers!
Why has our family forsaken us?
Join us, family. The Vault Thieves are winning!
Reinforcements! Hurry, before it's too late!
Brothers and sisters, we are saved!
Turn the tide. Kill the Vault Thieves!
Salvation at last! Now kill! KILL!
Tyreen has saved us! Now prove your worth!
More allies! We are the Children of the Vault!
Yes, NOW it's a fair fight!
Can't you do better than that?
Chase me and pay the price!
Don't chase me if you can't take the heat!
See ya, wouldn't wanna be ya!
Wait one second. This is personal.
Look away! I got a thing I gotta do!
The Great Vault awaits the COV!
Just try to get through me, heretic!
Take a real good look, Vault Thief!
Yeah! Time to get to work, fam!
Praise be! The Gods have sent an offering!
C'mere! Let's get you chopped up!
I am the spear of the Twin Gods!
I WILL have a place in the Great Vault!
Blast the heretic to tiny, TINY PIECES!
